This page lists the language bindings for DBus, their status and, if appropriate, links to download them.

== GLib ==

The GLib bindings are distributed with DBus.

== Python ==

The Python bindings are distributed with DBus.

== Qt4 ==

The Qt4 bindings are distributed with DBus.

== .NET ==

The .NET bindings are distributed with DBus.

== Java ==

There are two versions of the Java bindings. The Java 2 (1.4) bindings work with any free Java VM and Compiler and support most of the common DBus features. The Java 5 (1.5) bindings support all of the DBus features, but only work with 1.5-compatible VMs (Currently only Sun).

Documentation for the 1.5 Java bindings is available as [http://www.matthew.ath.cx/projects/dbus-doc/dbus-java/ HTML], [http://www.matthew.ath.cx/projects/dbus-doc/dbus-java.pdf PDF] and [http://www.matthew.ath.cx/projects/dbus-doc/dbus-java.ps PostScript]. [http://www.matthew.ath.cx/projects/dbus-doc/api/ Javadoc APIs] are also available. 

Documentation for the 1.4 bindings is available as [http://www.matthew.ath.cx/projects/dbus-doc-2/dbus-java/ HTML], [http://www.matthew.ath.cx/projects/dbus-doc-2/dbus-java.pdf PDF] and [http://www.matthew.ath.cx/projects/dbus-doc-2/dbus-java.ps PostScript]. [http://www.matthew.ath.cx/projects/dbus-doc-2/api/ Javadoc APIs] are also available. 

The Java Bindings can be downloaded here:

 * [http://www.matthew.ath.cx/projects/libdbus-java-1.0.tar.gz Java 1.5 Source] 
 * [http://www.matthew.ath.cx/projects/libdbus-java-0.2.tar.gz Java 1.4 Source]

The Maintainer is Matthew Johnson <dbus@matthew.ath.cx>

== Perl ==

The Perl bindings currently work on any Perl >= 5.8.x and any DBus version from 0.32.0 onwards. 
They can be downloaded from [http://search.cpan.org CPAN] under the [http://search.cpan.org/~danberr/Net-DBus-0.32.3/ Net-DBus] module:

 * [http://search.cpan.org/CPAN/authors/id/D/DA/DANBERR/Net-DBus-0.32.3.tar.gz Net-DBus-0.32.3.tar.gz]
 * [http://search.cpan.org/~danberr/Net-DBus-0.32.3/lib/Net/DBus.pm API documentation]
 * [http://search.cpan.org/~danberr/Net-DBus-0.32.3/lib/Net/DBus/Tutorial.pm Tutorials]

The maintainer is [http://search.cpan.org/~danberr/ Daniel P. Berrange]

